

= about PyLucid =

PyLucid is an Open Source (GPL v3) web content management system written in Python.

Official Homepage: http://www.pylucid.org



This is the "standalone" package, which contains all needed packages.

* simple move files via FTP on Webspace
* customize local_settings.py and .htaccess for your needs



Complete install instructions:

* http://www.pylucid.org/permalink/331/1b-install-pylucid-standalone-package



Informations about dependencies and copyrights:

* http://www.pylucid.org/permalink/41/dependencies-and-copyrights